You are here: Salesforce Help > Docs > Analytics > Access Dashboards on Record Layouts

Embed a dashboard on a record layout when you want to show an important insight every time your users open a record.

When you embed a dashboard on a record page (1), users tap to open the dashboard (2). When the dashboard opens (3), users can interact.
